import React from 'react';

import  ContentHeader  from '../../components/ContentHeader';
import  SelectInput  from '../../components/SelectInput';
import  SelectiMynaMonitoring   from '../../components/MynaMonitoring';

import { Container, Content } from './styles';
import MynaMonitoring from '../../components/MynaMonitoring';

const List: React.FC = () => {
    const options = [
        {value: 'rafa', label: 'rafa'},
        {value: 'charlie', label: 'charlie',}
    ];
    return (
        <Container>
        <ContentHeader title ="Outcomes" lineColor='#E44C4E'>
            <SelectInput options= {options} />
        </ContentHeader>
        <Content>
            <MynaMonitoring 
                tagColor = "#E44C4E"
                title = "Run 01"
                subtitle = "10/10/2024"
                status = "Success"
            />
            <MynaMonitoring 
                tagColor = "#E44C4E"
                title = "Run 02"
                subtitle = "11/11/2024"
                status = "Success"
            />

            <MynaMonitoring 
                tagColor = "#E44C4E"
                title = "Run 03"
                subtitle = "12/12/2024"
                status = "Success"
            />

            <MynaMonitoring 
                tagColor = "#E44C4E"
                title = "Run 04"
                subtitle = "13/13/2024"
                status = "Success"
            />

            <MynaMonitoring 
                tagColor = "#E44C4E"
                title = "Run 05"
                subtitle = "14/14/2024"
                status = "Success"
            />

            <MynaMonitoring 
                runColor = "#3138562"
                tagColor = "#E44C4E"
                title = "Run 06"
                subtitle = "15/15/2024"
                status = "Success"
            />

        </Content>

    </Container>
    );
    }
export default List;
